g%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Anh-t%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-GDec5vt9CaW448pIOKMKzQ">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Anh tài tử” - 奉和御製英才子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n/author-7XXX3GnZ0T6el9FCsBAeug">Ngô Hoán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-thi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba-v%C4%83n/poem-mgYAjQ2Q5NsDGZNtKtk96w">Tế thiên địa văn - 祭天地文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Ti%E1%BA%BFu-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-C4eOy8mqvNSyOkqKQJkQ-A">Tiếu hữu nhân - 誚友人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
